{{term|Weight map}}
{{defn|A set of Vertex attributes controlling deformation of a [[3D model]] during [[skeletal animation]]. Per-[[Vertex (computer graphics)|vertex]] [[Weighting|weights]] are assigned to control the influence of multiple bones (achieved by interpolating the transformations from each).<ref>{{cite web|title=weight maps|url=http://softimage.wiki.softimage.com/xsidocs/weightmaps_WeightMaps.htm}}</ref>
